Instant Quote Opportunity Process
     
1.       Details of this Instant Quote Opportunity are located at the OPPORTUNITIES tab of SunPower Partner Portal.
 
2.       Attached is the [satellite view of the location] and the [instant quote] for your convenience in assessing suitability during the initial stages of the evaluation.
 
3.       Please contact this instant quote opportunity within 24 hours and schedule a site visit accordingly (as required).
 
4.       Once you have contacted the opportunity, please update the OPPORTUNITY STAGE field in the SunPower Partner Portal- Opportunities Tab with “Opportunity Contacted”.  As subsequent tasks are completed please update the Opportunity as appropriate:
 
                        Visit Completed;
